      h3 Abbreviation: <code>#{'<abbr>'}</code>
      p: abbr title="Cascading Style Sheets" CSS 

      h3 Emphasis and strong: <code>#{'<em>'}</code> and  <code>#{'<strong>'}</code>
      p <em>Emphasis</em> and <strong>strong</strong>.

      h3 Code, samples, variables and inputs:  <code>#{'<code>'}</code>,  <code>#{'<samp>'}</code>,  <code>#{'<var>'}</code> and  <code>#{'<kbd>'}</code>
      p <code>This is code</code>, <samp>this is sample</samp>, <var>this is a variable</var> and <kbd>this is keyboard input</kbd>. Right now all of them looks the same.

