      p: s This is strikethrough

      h3 Cite: <code>#{'<cite>'}</code>
      p: cite This is a cite

      h3 Inline quotation: <code>#{'<q>'}</code>
      p <q> This is an inline quotation with a <q>nested quotation</q></q>. You are encouraged to replace default quotation marks for those of the language used in your document.

      h3 Definition: <code>#{'<dfn>'}</code>
      p <dfn>The definition</dfn> is given here.

      h3 Superscript and subscript: <code>#{'<sup>'}</code> and  <code>#{'<sub>'}</code>
      p Here we have a superscript<sup>1</sup> and here a subscript<sub>2</sub>.

      h3 <code>#{'<i>'}</code>, <code>#{'<b>'}</code> and <code>#{'<u>'}</code>
      p <i>This is <code>#{'<i>'}</code></i>, <b>this is <code>#{'<b>'}</code></b> and <u>this is <code>#{'<u>'}</code></u>.

      h3 Mark: <code>#{'<mark>'}</code>
      p: mark This is a mark

      h3 Insertions and deletions: <code>#{'<ins>'}</code> and  <code>#{'<del>'}</code>
      p <ins>This is an insertion</ins> and <del>this is a deletion</del>.

      h3 A line: <code>#{'<hr>'}</code>
      hr

      h2 Internals
      p The stylesheet is written in <a href="http://sass-lang.com/">Sass</a> and compiled to CSS. The main file is <code>src/gutenweb.sass</code>, which use <code>src/_print.sass</code>, where there are print styles, and the helper file <code>src/_helper.sass</code>, where there are some usefull functions and mixins.
      p <a href="http://meyerweb.com/eric/tools/css/reset/">Eric Meyer reset stylesheet</a> is also used to avoid problems with default rendering engines styles.
      p This page is written with <a href="http://slim-lang.com/">slim template language</a> (the <code>examples/index.html.slim</code> file) and compiled to html (the <code>examples/index.html</code> file).

      h2 Release Policy and version notes
      p Gutenweb uses <a href="http://semver.org/">semantic versioning system</a>. Now it is still at initial development.
      p It is sure that there are some common mark-up pattern that it is not covered. Please, <a href="https://github.com/waiting-for-dev/gutenweb/issues">open an issue</a> for any error or improvement you can suggest. It will be added as soon as possible.

